The Pro Secure team held a Women’s Day Placard demonstration on Thursday, 13 August at the Mobeni Heights intersection to show a united front against injustices on women. The team believes that amidst the celebrations of Women’s Month, they are determined to show their constant support towards the Chatsworth community with various stand offs and demonstrations within and around the area. Sales and Marketing Director, Rajen Govender said: “As a community based security company, our aim is to show our support and stand united in all fights against injustice. This month, residents can find our teams at various points creating awareness for Women’s Month.” The team further encourages the community and all women to stand up and join in the fight against all forms of abuse and injustice towards women.